oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Foo Fighters on the Concrete and Gold Tour at the Colonial Life Arena
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Foo Fighters (Musical group); Split Fountain Printing; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (gold and split fountain, periwinkle purple to light blue, on white) announcing the Concrete and Gold Tour starring the Foo Fighters at the Colonial Life Arena on October 17. Poster features a woodcut of spaceship over a neighborhood.
